Hi Volks,
See the 1963-67 "Workshop Manual Volkswagen Transporter", section K-2, page  
2.  The plug is to manufacture the ball check valve area.   Just above it is a 
pin which probably failed.  Pull out what is left of pin  and drop back in 
the ball.  Replace with new or good used pin.
Eric&Barb
